action.description: Declared an emergency measure under the Constitution.Read third time. Amended. (Amend. No. 22.)Dispensed with reprinting.Read third time. Passed, as amended. Title approved. (Yeas: 38, Nays: None, Excused: 3, Not voting: 1.)To printer.From printer. To reengrossment. Reengrossed. Second reprint.To Senate.In Senate.Assembly Amendment No. 22 concurred in. To enrollment.
